{"type": "article", "id": 32325, "title": "这些玻璃水瓶，究竟是满还是空？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-18T23:25:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32871, "name": "Fort Standard"}, {"id": 32872, "name": "mist-o"}, {"id": 32873, "name": "OTHR"}, {"id": 32874, "name": "Icendorf"}, {"id": 32875, "name": "BSX Athletics"}, {"id": 32876, "name": "Shirin Ehya"}, {"id": 32877, "name": "Hani Douaji"}, {"id": 32878, "name": "Fábio Silva"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 116, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160918235421Htudj2XPyk3DTSml.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Ico bottle opener by Fort Standard</h3><p>3D 打印家居品牌 <a href=\"https://www.othr.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OTHR</a> 在今年的纽约设计周上曾展出了一款由 <a href=\"http://fortstandard.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fort Standard</a> 工作室设计的青铜 3D 打印开瓶器 Ico，独特的造型颠覆了人们对开瓶器的刻板印象，可以当作小摆设一直放在桌面上。它的外观是一个独特的二十面体，每一面都能用来开启瓶盖，而且脱落的瓶盖刚好会留在开瓶器内。最近在 OTHR 在这款畅销产品的基础上又推出了采用哑光黑的钢材制作而成的限量版，这是它的<a href=\"https://www.othr.com/products/ico-bottle-opener-limited-edition\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 120 美元。你还可以通过<a href=\"https://www.othr.com/products/ico-bottle-opener/37\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到青铜版，售价为 70 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000032YrmNPIn2QtsUVDuZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000032n6W5bOIipCskHRey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000032Oe0CH2otRzQgpXcl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000032s7c6ex8KFXp0hnia.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000032gSytkHnTWMb0O5mC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000032GPFRZQrtJcHz2bBf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fantasia Collection by Shirin Ehya</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.ehyadesignstudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shirin Ehya</a> 是一位美籍伊朗裔设计师，这套名为 <a href=\"http://www.ehyadesignstudio.com/fantasia/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fantasia</a> 的家具系列就是她根据波斯镶边陶瓷装饰工艺 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cuerda_seca\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cuerda Seca</a> 为灵感创作的，光滑的漆木表面是由激光切割而成的图案，充满了浓郁的异域风情。为了突出花纹的复杂与精细度，波斯陶瓷工匠只会使用七种饱满而鲜活的颜色，这一特点也被 Ehya 沿用了下来。目前这套家具正在巴黎玛莱区的 <a href=\"http://galeriejoseph.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joseph 画廊</a>展出。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000135DWNnH4uYOfiLEB2s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609190001357uIpZkslTiDanHLR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000136gw1DFm42WQfIhuKb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000136aNJbKH2Pj0YT7cet.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000137KkWwc3zINoFs2m45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160919000136m1ACvqS0P58QWOxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658924\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Juice by Hani Douaji</h3><p>出门在外，手机马上就要没电还没有移动电源可用的情况总是让人焦虑，英国的黎巴嫩裔概念视觉设计师 <a href=\"http://www.hanidouaji.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hani Douaji</a> 最近就针对这一特殊时刻设计了一款名为 <a href=\"http://www.hanidouaji.com/Juice\" rel=\"nofollow\">Juice</a> 的一次性移动电源，就像是为手机量身打造的“果汁”。它和我们曾经介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/3600.html\">迷你型电源</a>有异曲同工之妙，携带起来非常方便。兼容 iPhone 与安卓设备的 Juice 最长能够使用四个小时，可以将手机的电量从 0 充至 40%。Douaji 还为 Juice 设计了一款简洁明了的外包装，两角处分别印有渐变色的闪电图案。目前 Juice 还处于概念设计阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235935dnupct0wSOG9UJvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235935J32tBLfxFv7H5Zmz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609182359359OEwi0CjBgzcr45x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609182359354IhNwD7AS3aFtUdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235935aFsrV5gET1bXxL2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235935GdLxIVjwis2Ca8WS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tequila Sunrise Carafe Collection by mist-o</h3><p>第一眼看到由双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.mist-o.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">mist-o</a> 与意大利玻璃制造商 <a href=\"http://www.ichendorfmilano.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Icendorf</a> 带来的 <a href=\"http://www.mist-o.com/index.php/work/tequila-sunrise/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tequila Sunrise 玻璃水瓶</a>时，你或许很难分辨出它们究竟是空还是满。为了创造出这种微妙的平衡感，两位设计师将不同类型的硼酸玻璃拼接在了一起。这种工艺能够在保持外观通透的同时使容器看上去像是已经装有液体一样，带给人一种独特的视觉效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609182359042CL69V1I5H37Daiu.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235904ejo6EZuS1iXl9JRt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235904zkL7IyuhPw9U0f6r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609182359040Pvalt1oAz7FLXes.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235904ZpiG9yAaSbsgOPxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235904KH7qhAsyJtf1cvkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.044010\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235905UReqSMu1jmxr642h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.806846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LVL by BSX Athletics</h3><p>测量心率、记录运动量、监测卡路里消耗和睡眠质量……市面上不少智能手环都具备了这些围绕人体健康为核心的功能，而在美国穿戴式传感器公司 <a href=\"https://www.bsxinsight.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BSX Athletics</a> 的设计师眼中，这些产品缺少了一项与健康息息相关的监测项目，即人体的水合状态。为了提醒人们饮水的重要性，设计团队为旗下的 LVL 智能手环研发了一种特殊的红光传感器，这种红光的穿透能力是传统手环所使用的绿光的十倍，能够帮助人们更准确地获悉各项健康数据。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lactate-threshold/lvl-the-first-wearable-hydration-monitor\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 119 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235703WfJk2xPKB4ynTjm6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.586765\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235701QTdqtONU5XhLDi3m.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.530882\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235702h58USXvCgzfVlJqy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.077941\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235706pA4Faow7PKqLBrek.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.214706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235705vIx0bsoJKlYEHgAS.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.895588\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>EGG by Fábio Silva</h3><p>设计师们总能从琐碎的生活细节中获得启发，来自西班牙的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/fabio-silva\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fábio Silva</a> 最近就以破碎的鸡蛋为灵感，设计了一款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42804197/EGG\" rel=\"nofollow\">EGG</a> 的三脚凳。白色的聚丙烯座位是它的“蛋壳”，“蛋黄”的部分是一块黄色的皮革坐垫。“鸡蛋”下方通过一个可以调节高度的铝制结构与三根木制椅腿相连，外形简单却不失趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235446ZAXx6k2io9MWaCKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235447DTrECYUVOBM6KWaP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609182354464K7u2eo9ftlhvOMP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235444a3xYPdKe5ic2sMjh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235446uG6lzdJ1erZ9i70E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160918235447rXQNTicZpVtCynAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}